flowchart TD
    Task[Incoming task] --> Intent[Clarify intent]
    Intent --> Scope[Define scope and non-goals]
    Scope --> Risk[Assess risk]
    Risk --> Duration[Estimate duration / complexity]
    Duration --> Uncertainty[Assess uncertainty]
    Uncertainty --> Approval[Check approval boundaries]

    Approval --> Decision{Recommended route}

    Decision --> L0[L0 Direct<br/>small local change]
    Decision --> L1[L1 Micro-plan<br/>short multi-step task]
    Decision --> L2[L2 Plan iterations<br/>multi-step implementation]
    Decision --> L3[L3 Independent checks<br/>audit / review / research]
    Decision --> L4[L4 Route exploration<br/>architecture comparison]
    Decision --> L5[L5 Deep branching<br/>prototype / high uncertainty]

    L0 --> Execute[Execute with minimal overhead]
    L1 --> MicroPlan[State short plan, then execute]
    L2 --> Checkpoints[Execute through checkpoints]
    L3 --> Report[Produce findings/report]
    L4 --> Options[Compare routes before choosing]
    L5 --> Branches[Explore branches, prototypes, trade-offs]

    Execute --> Validate[Validation / result]
    MicroPlan --> Validate
    Checkpoints --> Validate
    Report --> Review[Human review]
    Options --> Review
    Branches --> Review
